      "content": "pool oscillation makes sense. but even with the traffic being flat, it feels almost like something is randomly stealing resources or just being chaotic for no reason. it's super annoying for the on-call team.\n\nbesides the pool size, are there any other weird edge cases in the driver or the way the app handles connection timeouts that could cause this kind of unpredictable \"bursty\" latency?",
